                    </opener>
                    <p>Rafael Acosta, Martinez Hurtado, Molina Ramos, Perez Lopez, Monteagudo
                        Chanes, Martinez Rodriguez, Rodriguez Romero, Cuadra Cardona, wife, three
                        children, colored.</p>
                    <closer>
